title: EXT_AUTHN_NOT_ENROLLED
description: User is not enrolled in Duo Security. Contact your local system administrator.

title: EXT_AUTHN_LOCKED
description: User is locked from Duo Security. Contact your local system administrator.

title: EXT_AUTHN_SMS_SENT
description: Duo Security temporary passcode is sent via SMS. Please authenticate using the passcode.

title: EXT_AUTHN_TIMEOUT
description: Timed out waiting for your login request approval via Duo Mobile. If your mobile device has no data service
column4: generate a Duo passcode and enter it in the connect string.

title: EXT_AUTHN_EXCEPTION
description: Request could not be completed due to a communication problem with the external service provider. Try again later.

title: EXT_AUTHN_DUO_PUSH_DISABLED
description: Duo Push is not enabled for your MFA. Provide a passcode as part of the connection string.

title: FED_REAUTH_PENDING
description: Authentication response is pending from IDP.

title: FED_REAUTH
description: Federated authentication request URL is generated.

title: FED_REAUTH_TIMEOUT
description: Timeout waiting for authentication response from IDP.

title: AUTHENTICATOR_NOT_SUPPORTED
description: The specified authenticator is not accepted by your Snowflake account configuration. Please contact your local system administrator to get the correct URL to use.

title: FED_PASSWORD_EXPIRED
description: Identity Provider (IdP) password has expired. Contact your IdP team.

title: USERNAMES_MISMATCH
description: The user you were trying to authenticate as differs from the user currently logged in at the IDP.
